A citizen presents a gun when faced with a crime, and the perp runs away. The citizen either doesn’t call the police. Or they do call but are told that since it’s not an active crime scene, it may be an hour or two before an officer responds, and the citizen having better things to do, declines to have an officer take a report. Therefore, the MSM has no way of knowing it happened
